# Ignore build results
**/[Bb]in
**/[Oo]bj

# Ignore Visual Studio Code
**/.vscode

# Ignore Visual Studio
**/.vs

# NuGet Packages
# The packages folder can be ignored. Use package restore
**/packages/*

# Ignore user-specific files
*.suo
*.user

# Ignore directory meta info as created by KDE
.directory

# Ignore JetBrains Rider / IntelliJ IDEA meta info
.idea

# Ignore swap files
*.swp

# Ignore Mono runtime crash reports — written when net472/net48/net481
# test executables crash under Mono on non-Windows hosts. Diagnostic
# artefacts, not test failures (the tests themselves still pass).
mono_crash.*.json
